# Billionaire Brother — Costing Guardrails Summary

> Status: **Active & Enforced** • Model: **Gemini 3 Pro Preview** • Last Updated: March 2026

---

## Tier Entitlements

| Guard | Brother ($39→$49) | Team ($99→$129) |
|:---|:---:|:---:|
| **Daily Prompts** | 40 | 100 |
| **Max Output Tokens** | 4,096 | 8,192 |
| **Degrade Output Tokens** | 2,048 | 4,096 |
| **Workflow Steps** | 6 | 10 |
| **Weekly Regenerations** | 2 | 4 |
| **Monthly Dollar Cap** (budget) | $50.00 | $150.00 |
| **Web Search** | ❌ | ❌ (Phase 2+) |
| **Tool Calls** | ❌ | ❌ (Phase 2+) |

---

## Per-Request Guardrails

| Control | Value |
|:---|:---|
| **Output token hard cap** | Enforced via `maxOutputTokens` in Gemini SDK |
| **Max retries per step** | 2 (fail fast + diagnostics) |
| **Retry delay** | 1s → 2s → 4s (exponential backoff) |
| **Tool calls per request** | 0 (disabled Phase 1) |
| **ThinkingConfig** | HIGH (strategy/ship-pack) · MEDIUM (tasks/checkin) · LOW (chat/interview) |

---

## Circuit Breakers

| Threshold | % of Cap | Brother Trigger | Team Trigger | System Response |
|:---|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---|
| **Warning** | 60% | $30.00 | $90.00 | Alert logged (deduplicated monthly) |
| **Degrade** | 80% | $40.00 | $120.00 | Halve output tokens, block regens, user banner |
| **Hard Stop** | 100% | $50.00 | $150.00 | Block all AI requests until billing reset |

User-facing messaging:
- **80%**: "You're approaching your sprint budget. Focus on execution."
- **95%**: "Sprint budget almost reached. Responses will be simplified."
- **100%**: "Sprint budget reached. Resets [date]. Focus on execution."

---

## Cost Estimation Engine

| Pricing Layer | Input / 1M Tokens | Output / 1M Tokens | Purpose |
|:---|:---:|:---:|:---|
| **Actual** | $1.25 | $10.00 | Financial reporting |
| **Budget (2.5× safety)** | $3.125 | $25.00 | Cap enforcement & alerts |

Every AI request logs: model, input tokens, output tokens, latency, endpoint, tier, degrade mode, estimated cost.

---

## Metering Layers

| Layer | Table | Tracked |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Per-request** | `request_logs` | model, tokens, latency, cost, endpoint, tier |
| **Per-user daily** | `usage_daily_user` | prompt count, tokens, regens, workflows, cost |
| **Per-user weekly** | `usage_weekly_user` | regen count |
| **Per-workspace monthly** | `usage_monthly_workspace` | total tokens, prompts, cost, regen usage |
| **Alerts** | `cost_alerts` | type, threshold %, values, resolution |

All counters use **atomic PL/pgSQL upsert RPCs** to prevent race conditions.

---

## Bounded Workflow Engine

| Workflow | Max Steps | Retry/Step | Tools |
|:---|:---:|:---:|:---:|
| Revenue Bottleneck Diagnosis | 3 | 2 | None |
| Revenue Path Ranking | 4 | 2 | None |
| Sprint Pack Builder | 6 | 2 | None |
| KPI Spec Generator | 3 | 2 | None |
| Kill/Keep/Double | 4 | 2 | None |

Budget exceeded → `"Workflow exceeded sprint budget. Simplify request."`

---

## Kill Switches

| Switch | Scope |
|:---|:---|
| `ai_layer` | All AI requests globally |
| `workflows` | All multi-step workflows |
| `tools` | All tool/search calls |

Checked **before every AI request** via the middleware pipeline.

---

## Middleware Pipeline (compose.ts)

```
Request → Kill Switch → Subscription Lookup → Usage Guard → Token Budget → AI Call → Meter Logger → Response
```

If any gate fails → `GuardError` with user-friendly message + HTTP 429.

---

