| Metric | Value |
|:---|:---|
| Blended revenue/user | ~$73/month |
| Budget safety margin | 2.5× actual pricing |
| Target gross margin | ≥ 85% |
| At 10,000 users: Revenue | ~$730k/month |
| At 10,000 users: Max AI cost | ~$60k/month |
| At 10,000 users: Margin | ~92% |

