## What We Don't Build

- ❌ Autonomous "run my business" loops
- ❌ Open-ended multi-hour workflows
- ❌ Unrestricted research scraping
- ❌ Unlimited regeneration
- ❌ Free text mega-prompts
- ❌ Unmetered tool calls

**Margin > ego. Always.**
